data.description: Welcome Home to this superbly constructed 2104 ft.², four bedroom 3 1/2 bath, ranch style, one story home, nestled in the Meadowbrook Village section of Newport. Situated in the soft rolling hills near Jackson Bayou. This home, by CastleRock Communities was built and completed in late 2019 and features a grand entry way with coffered ceilings, and crown molding. Along the main entryway are 3 secondary bedrooms with 2 full baths and a guest bathroom. Providing full quarters for a sizable family and guests without breaking the budget. Many upgrades include Granite Kitchen with an abundance of oversized cabinets, and marble countertops throughout. An extended covered rear patio area provides private relaxation and overlooks a forest behind the home. Just inside is a cozy gas fireplace centrally located in the main family room.  The generous size of the owners suite gives privacy and quiet solitude to its owners and includes a luxurious & large soaking tub, separate shower and twin vanities. A large walk-in wardrobe closet gives plenty of room for clothes, shoes and other items. This well built cozy home is priced to sell and wont last.
